data.description:
Light and bright 2-Story with main-level master in secure, gated community.  Open floor plan with hardwood floors, great room with fireplace and soaring ceiling, kitchen, main-level laundry, and walk-out to brand new deck.  Upper level features loft with two bedrooms and full bath.  Finished basement with family room, two more spacious bedrooms, and another bath.  HOA maintains exterior stucco and roof, fees include insurance, lawn maintenance, trash and snow removal.  Mountain views and attached 2-car garage. 
Listing Agent: Joseph J.
Company: RE/MAX Properties, Inc.
Phone: 719-304-4929
Email: clementrealestate@wesellmore.net
